# Mac OS X升级Git 1.8.4.2

检查git版本

    git --version

检查hombrew git版本

    brew info git

升级git版本

    brew upgrade git

出错处理

    Error: The `brew link` step did not complete successfully
    The formula built, but is not symlinked into /usr/local
    You can try again using `brew link git'

修改/usr/local/bin和/usr/local/lib/python2.7/site-packages/git_remote_helpers的属性

    sudo chown your_user_name:your_user_group /usr/local/bin
    sudo chown your_user_name:your_user_group /usr/local/lib/python2.7/site-packages/git_remote_helpers

